data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning craftsman-style residence is a true embodiment of comfort and style. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this 2-story gem offers a perfect blend of space and sophistication. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the abundance of storage solutions throughout the home. The kitchen, a culinary enthusiast's delight, features not only a well-appointed pantry but also a second pantry for added convenience. The master bathroom is a haven of organization with custom closets, providing ample space for your wardrobe. The entire house has been tastefully upgraded with modern touches that enhance its overall charm. Revel in the beauty of the new backsplash and granite counters in the kitchen, creating a sleek and contemporary atmosphere. The bright and airy paint colors throughout the home infuse each room with a sense of openness and tranquility. But the enhancements don't stop indoors – step outside to discover the newly paved patio area, perfect for entertaining or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars. Your little ones will delight in the children's playset, making the backyard a true haven for family fun. Safety is a top priority with the inclusion of an ADT alarm system seamlessly linked to the fire alarm, providing you with peace of mind. This state-of-the-art security system conveys with the home, offering an added layer of protection. And that's not all – this community also features a refreshing community pool, providing you with a perfect retreat for relaxation and socializing. Not to be overlooked, the garage features additional overhead space, ensuring that every inch of this home is optimized for your convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this craftsman masterpiece your own – a perfect blend of modern luxury, timeless elegance, and community amenities awaits you!
